          { "feature": "severe_withdrawal_on_cessation", "weight": 3 }
        ],
        "management": "Methadone maintenance or buprenorphine/naloxone. Supervised daily dispensing initially. Harm reduction: needle exchange, naloxone kit. Hepatitis C/HIV screening. Psychosocial support."
